29 January 2016Cabinet will hold its Lekgotla from the 02 to the 06 of February 2016 at Sefako Makgatho Presidential Guesthouse in Pretoria.Members of the media will be allowed a brief opportunity to take pictures of Cabinet members. This will be followed by an equally brief engagement with the Minister in the Presidency responsible for Performance, Monitoring and Evaluation, Mr Jeff Radebe.The details of the photo opportunity are:Date: Tuesday, 2 February 2016 Time: To be confirmed Venue: Sefako Makgatho Presidential Guesthouse in Pretoria (access through Gate 10)NB: There is an accreditation process for all media attending. Media who have not accredited will not be granted access.Kindly send the confirmation of attendance to Ishmael@gcis.gov.za with details as per the table below. The deadline for submission is 12h00 on Monday. Please bring along an ID/Passport as well as a Press Card where applicable.Enquiries: Phumla Williams Cell: 083 501 0139Issued by GCIS